\id 1TI
\h 1 Timutiyu 
\toc1 1 Timutiyu 
\toc2 1 Timutiyu 
\toc3 1 Tim. 
\mt1 1 Timutiyu  
\c 1
\s1 Aseǧem ɣar umezwaru d iɛřamen  
\m
\v 1 Bulus, rrasul n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, ɛlaḥsab řumur n AREBBI, wenni d aneɣ itticen Tudart, u n Lmasiḥ Yasuɛ, wenni d asitem nneɣ. \f ◼ \fr 1:1 \ft \+fk rrasul\ft  - niɣ ‘amazan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Řex. 9:15; Kul. 1:27. \x*  
\v 2 I Timutiyu, mmi d tidett di l’iman: arḍa d arreḥmet d řehna \add ad ac iřin\add* zi AREBBI, Babatneɣ, u zi Lmasiḥ Yasuɛ, Siditneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Řex. 16:1; 1 Kur. 4:17; Gal. 1:3; 1 Ts. 3:2; 1 Bṭ. 1:2. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 3 Řami ruḥeɣ ɣar Makiduniya zawgeɣ cek ad teqqimed di Afasus, ḥima ad tumured i ca n yeryazen ḥima war sseřmiden ca iseřmaden nneɣni, \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Řex. 20:1. \x*  
\v 4 \add u\add* ḥima war tticen ca taynit i tḥuja ixwan d taṣiřat war iqeṭṭin nni dd-ittawyen ɣar imḥarwaḍen ktar, war iǧi ɣar min iǧan i řebni di l’iman n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt 1 Tim. 4:7; 6:4, 20; 2 Tim. 2:16; Tit. 1:14; 3:9. \x*  
\v 5 Ssum n tweṣṣa aqa d tayri zeg wuř amezdag d tnefsect icnan u zi l’iman d tidett. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Rum. 13:8; Gal. 5:14. \x*  
\v 6 Aqa dinni ca inni iheyyḍen x man aya uca nnqeřben ɣar řhard ixwan.  
\v 7 Nitni xsen ad iřin d imesɣaren n Ccariɛa břa řefhamet di min qqaren u x min xef ttemcubbucen.  
\v 8 Maca nessen belli Ccariɛa teṣbeḥ mařa ḥed ijja ixef nnes ad ittwandeh zzayes ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa, \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Rum. 7:12. \x*  
\v 9 am nessen aqa Ccariɛa war temmewc ca i umseggaden, maca i yinni war iseggden u i imɣewwaɣen, i iɛeffanen d imednab, i imeqjaḥ, i imexmujen, i yinni iwtin babatsen u i yinni iwtin yemmatsen u i yinni ineqqen \add iwdan\add*, \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Gal. 5:23. \x*  
\v 10 i ayt n farq-ccɣeř d zzwameř, i yinni ittsebbaben deg iwdan, i ayt n bu-ixarriqen d yinni ittareẓẓan tajaǧit nsen uca zeɛma i marra min war dd-ittisen ca ak-d useřmed iṣeḥḥen  
\v 11 n L’Injil i d ayi ittwawekkřen, zi jjihet n uɛuǧi n AREBBI ittwabarken. \x ◘ \xo 1:11 \xt 1 Ts. 2:4; 1 Tim. 6:15. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Arḍa n Arebbi i Bulus  
\m
\v 12 Necc ttqadiɣ Wenni d ayi issjehden, aqa Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, umi iḥseb ayi-dd d amtiqqi řami d ayi igga di řxedmet n tsexxart \add nnes\add*,  
\v 13 necc d wenni tuɣa iǧan qbeř d amceqqaf d ijj n umarrat \add n imasiḥiyyen\add* uřa d ijj n bu-řɛunf. Maca temmewc ayi-dd arreḥmet, minzi ggiɣ t war ssineɣ, \add umi d ayi tuɣa\add* břa l’iman. \x ◘ \xo 1:13 \xt Yḥ. 9:39,41; Řex. 3:17; 8:3; 9:1; 22:4; 26:9; 1 Kur. 15:9; Gal. 1:13. \x*  
\v 14 Arḍa n Siditneɣ tuɣa ifeyyeḍ dayi s waṭṭas, uřa d l’iman d tayri tenni iǧan di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.  
\v 15 Wa d awař dayes řaman, i isdaheǧen ad yiři iggur, aqa Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ yusa-dd ɣar ddunect ḥima ad issenjem imednab, inni zzaysen necc d amezwaru. \x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt Mt. 9:13; Mk. 2:17; Lk. 5:32; 19:10; 1 Yḥ. 3:5. \x*  
\v 16 Maca x uya ksiɣ arreḥmet maḥend Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ad isscen dayi d amezwaru marra ttasiɛ n řxaḍar nnes, d lmital i yinni zzayes i ɣa yamnen i Tudart ittduman.   
\m
\v 17 Aqa i Ujeǧid n zzmanat, d Wenni war ifennin, d Wenni war ittwiřin, Wenni d AREBBI d Ijj, ad ɣares yiři ccan d uɛuǧi i zzman n zzmanat qaɛ. Amin. \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt 1 Tim. 6:16\x*   
\m
\v 18 Tasexxart-a, \add a\add* mmi Timutiyu, sswekkřeɣ cek xas, ḥima ad temmenɣed amenɣi aṣebḥan ɛlaḥsab min xak ittwanabben qbeř, \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt 1 Tim. 6:12. \x*  
\v 19 s l’iman d tnefsect icnan, maɣar inni ugin man aya, aqa ssexwan ixef nsen zi l’iman. \x ◘ \xo 1:19 \xt 1 Tim. 3:9. \x*  
\v 20 Jar asen Himiniyus d Aliksandir, inni sellmeɣ i cciṭan ḥima ad řemden maḥend war ttceqqafen. \x ◘ \xo 1:20 \xt 1 Kur. 5:5; 2 Tim. 2:17; 4:14. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Aseřmed n Bulus x weɛbad n tmesmunt i Arebbi  
\m
\v 1 S uyenni ttzawageɣ kenniw, ḥima ad tqarrbem d amezwaru ɣar AREBBI s tutra d tẓaǧitin d tkessit s řmeɛruf d uqadi di ṭṭweɛ n marra iwdan,  
\v 2 di ṭṭweɛ n ijeǧiden d imeqqranen, ḥima xenni ad neddar di řehna d řhudnet u s marra tiggʷudi d tezdugi zzat AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Irm. 29:7. \x*  
\v 3 Minzi man aya d aṣebḥan u yusa as-dd i řxaḍar i AREBBI, wenni d aneɣ itticen Tudart,  
\v 4 wenni ixsen aqa marra iwdan ad ṭṭfen Tudart uca ad dd-dewřen ɣar tussna n tidett. \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt Ḥiz. 18:23; 2 Bṭ. 3:9. \x*  
\v 5 Minzi aqa din ijj n AREBBI d ijj n Lwasit jar AREBBI d iwdan, aqa Netta d Mmis n bnadem, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Yḥ. 17:3; Rum. 3:30; Gal. 3:19; Ɛbr. 9:15. \x*  
\v 6 wenni iwcin Ixef nnes d aṣřaḥ i marra bnadem, aqa-tt d cchadet i dd-yusin di řweqt nnes. \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Mt. 20:28; Afa. 1:7; Kul. 1:14. \x*  
\v 7 I man aya ttwaggeɣ d ambarreḥ d rrasul, aqa qqareɣ tidett, war ssxarriqeɣ ca, ḥima ad iřiɣ d amseɣɣar n řegnus di l’iman n tidett. \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt Řex. 9:15; 13:2; 22:21; Rum. 1:9; 9:1; Gal. 1:16; 2:8; Afa. 3:8; 2 Tim. 1:11. \x*   
\m
\v 8 S uya xseɣ belli iryazen ad ẓẓaǧen di mkuř amcan, am ssgeɛɛaden ifassen nsen s tezdugi, břa axeyyeq d umcubbec. \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt Izhd. 134:2; Yḥ. 4:21. \x*   
\m
\v 9 Ammu uřa d timɣarin ad yarḍent s uweqqar, ittxeṣṣa ad zehhjent ixef nsent s ijj n webrid n řeḥya u n tsexxayt, war iǧi s umudi n ucuwwaf niɣ s wureɣ niɣ s tyaqutin niɣ s warruḍ iɣřan, \x ◘ \xo 2:9 \xt Tit. 2:3; 1 Bṭ. 3:3. \x*  
\v 10 maca \add ad zehhjent ixef nsent\add* s řexdayem iṣebḥen am mammec dd-yusa x temɣarin, tinni ittnejbaden ɣar uweqqar n AREBBI.   
\m
\v 11 Ejj tamɣart ad teřmed di řhudnet, ak-d marra tamwaḍeɛt,  
\v 12 maca necc war ttejjiɣ tamɣart ad tesseřmed niɣ ad ɣares yiři jjehd x weryaz, maca ad tiři tesqar. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Amz. 3:16; 1 Kur. 14:34; Afa. 5:24. \x*  
\v 13 Minzi Adam ittwagg d amezwar, awarni as Ḥawwa. \x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt Amz. 1:27; 2:22. \x*  
\v 14 Uca Adam war ittwaɣarr ca, maca tamɣart tᵉttwaɣarr, xenni texḍa x tewṣeyyet. \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Amz. 3:6. \x*  
\v 15 Maca ad teddar s tarwa nnes, mařa ttɣiman nitni ttcebbaren di l’iman d tayri d tqeddast d řeḥya.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Imeḥḍayen d imseyyaren n tmesmunt  
\m
\v 1 Wa d awař dayes řaman: mařa ixs ḥed ad yiři d amɣar, aqa ittmeẓri deg ict n řxedmet tecna.  
\v 2 Maca ittxeṣṣa i umɣar ad itwaf břa řɛib, ad yiři d aryaz n ict n temɣart, ɣares amekken n nnefs, ad yiři d asexxay, ad igg s usettef, ad yareḥḥeb s inewjiwen, izemmar ad isseřmed. \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt 2 Tim. 2:24; Tit. 1:6. \x*  
\v 3 Netta war ittiři d amescar niɣ iwwet deɣya s ufus nnes, maca ad yiři d amwaḍeɛ, war ittemcubbuc, war ittiři d aqezzaz.  
\v 4 Aqa netta isseggur taddart nnes mliḥ uca iḥekkem x iḥenjiren nnes s marra řeṣfayet.  
\v 5 Maca mařa netta war izemmar ad issuyur taddart nnes, mammec ɣa igg ad iḥḍa tamesmunt n AREBBI?  
\v 6 War ittiři d ameḥḍar n jdid \add di l’iman\add*, ḥima war ittuff \add s řefyuc\add* uca ad iwḍa di ccreɛ n cciṭan.  
\v 7 Ɛawed ittxeṣṣa ad ɣares tiři ṣṣumɛet tecna ɣar yinni di barra, ḥima war xas ttɛeyyiben uca war iweṭṭi ca di řefxux n cciṭan.   
\m
\v 8 Ittxeṣṣa ɛawed i imsexxaren \add di tmesmunt\add* ad iřin d imezdagen, war ssiwiřen ca s tnayen n iřsawen, war xezzaren ca ɣar binu aṭṭas, war ḍemmɛen di arrbeḥ war iḥřin. \x ◘ \xo 3:8 \xt Řex. 6:3. \x*  
\v 9 Ittxeṣṣa asen ad ṭṭfen di ssirr n l’iman s tnefsect teṣfa. \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt 1 Tim. 1:19. \x*  
\v 10 Ejj i-ten ad ttwaqeǧben d amezwaru, řexdenni, mařa iban-dd war daysen ittiři bu řɛib, ad sexxaren.  
\v 11 Ammu ittxeṣṣa uřa i timɣarin ad arsint s tsexxayt, ad ḥḍant di řeɛquř nsent, ad daysent tiři řmanet di marra, war d ttiřint d timceqqafin.  
\v 12 Ittxeṣṣa i imsexxaren \add di tmesmunt\add*, aqa \add kuř ijjen zzaysen\add* ad yiři s ict n temɣart, uca ittxesṣa as ad issuyur mliḥ iḥenjiren nnes d taddart nnes.  
\v 13 Minzi inni itteggen taseyyart nsen mliḥ, ad ṭṭfen i yixef nsen ijj n wemcan icna d waṭṭas n teryast di l’iman n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Mt. 25:21. \x*   
\m
\v 14 Uriɣ ac-dd man aya uca ssitimeɣ ad ɣarek dd-aseɣ deɣya.  
\v 15 Maca mařa ɛeṭṭařeɣ xak, ad tessned mammec ittxeṣṣa ad nuyur di taddart n AREBBI, tenni iǧan d Tamesmunt n AREBBI iddaren, apilar d dsas n tidett. \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt Afa. 2:19; Ɛbr. 10:21; 1 Bṭ. 4:17\x*  
\v 16 Ssirr wanita n tsegda d ameqqran s tidett!  
\b  
\m \qt “D Wenni ittwassargben di ddat,\qt*  
\m \qt ittwaseggden di Arruḥ,\qt*  
\m \qt iḍḥaren-dd i lmalakat,\qt*  
\m \qt ittwabarrḥen zzayes jar řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt d Wenni \+tl zzayes\+tl* yumnen di ddunect,\qt*  
\m \qt immeksin deg uɛuǧi.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:16 \xt Mk. 16:19; Lk. 9:51; Yḥ. 1:14; Řex. 1:2; Afa. 3:5, 6. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Uqarri n ccayaṭin d thuja tibuhařiyyen  
\m
\v 1 Maca Arruḥ iqqar nican belli di zzmanat tineggura ca ad ḥeyyden x l’iman umi ɣa ḍfaren řaryaḥ issɣekkwan d tɣuri n ccwaṭen. \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Mt. 24:23; 2 Ts. 2:3; 2 Tim. 3:1; 2 Bṭ. 3:3; Yah. 18. \x*  
\v 2 Nitni sɣekkwan am ssniɛmiřen ixef nsen, ssxarriqen u tteqqden tanefsect nsen.  
\v 3 Nitni ttᵉṭṭfen řemřac uca ttamaren asbeɛɛed x macca nni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi AREBBI maḥend ad tiři i nnfeɛ d uqadi i yinni yumnen u ssnen tidett. \x ◘ \xo 4:3 \xt Amz. 1:29; 9:3; Rum. 14:6; 1 Kur. 10:30. \x*  
\v 4 Minzi marra min dd-ittwaxeřqen zi AREBBI iṣbeḥ uca war dayes min ɣa nagi mařa neqbeř zzayes s uqadi, \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt Amz. 1:31; Řex. 10:15; Rum. 14:14. \x*  
\v 5 minzi ad ittwaqeddes s Wawař n AREBBI d tẓaǧit.   
\b  
\m
\v 6 Mařa tessřemded man aya i wawmaten nnec, ad tiřid d amsexxar n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, aqa tᵉttwarebbid deg wawařen n l’iman u tᵉttwassřemded di tɣuri n ṣṣaḥ. \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt 2 Tim. 1:5; 3:14, 15. \x*  
\v 7 Maca aggʷej x tḥuja ixwan n twessura u marres ixef nnec di tsegda. \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt 1 Tim. 1:4; 6:20; 2 Tim. 2:16; Tit. 1:14; 3:9. \x*  
\v 8 Minzi arriyaḍa n arrimet tᵉttawi ɣar nnfaɛ i drus n řweqt waha, maca tasegda tneffeɛ řebda, uca aqa ɣares lwaɛd n Tudart i yiḍa u i řweqt i dd ɣa yasen. \x ◘ \xo 4:8 \xt Kul. 2:23. \x*   
\m
\v 9 Wa d awař dayes řaman, isdaheǧ ad ittwaqbeř.  
\v 10 Minzi i man aya umi nxeddem u nettwasseḥqara ɛawed, minzi asitem nneɣ aqa-t di AREBBI iddaren, wenni itticen Tudart i marra iwdan, amezwaru i yinni yumnen.  
\v 11 Seřmed, tumured s man aya.   
\m
\v 12 Ejj uřa d ijj war cek isseḥqiri ca x temẓi nnec, maca iři d lmital i yinni yumnen, s wawař, s wendah, s tayri, s l’iman u s tazdugi. \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Tit. 2:7, 15; 1 Bṭ. 5:3. \x*  
\v 13 Iři tecḍared di tɣuri \add i tmesmunt\add*, di ṭẓaǧit u deg useřmed ař dd ɣa yaseɣ.  
\v 14 War sḥeqqara ca tawhibt i dayek, tenni i d ac immewcen umi tuɣa ttnabben u ssarsen imɣaren xak ifassen. \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt Řex. 6:6; 8:17; 13:3; 19:6; 1 Tim. 5:22; 2 Tim. 1:6. \x*  
\v 15 Ɛqeř x tmesřayin-a, cebbar daysent, ḥima ticři nnec ɣar zzat ad tban i marra.  
\v 16 Ḥḍa ixef nnec u ḥḍa x useřmed, ṣbar di man aya, minzi mařa teggid ddegga, ad teḥḍid ixef nnec di Tudart uřa d inni d ac ittesřan.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 X udebbar n tmesmunt  
\m
\v 1 War tiřid tewɛared i uwessar, maca nesḥ i-t am babac, uca ibřiɣen am wawmaten nnec, \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt Lawi 19:32. \x*  
\v 2 tiwessura am tiyemmatin, uca tiɛezriyyin am suyᵉtmac nnec, s marra řeṣfayet.   
\m
\v 3 Weqqar tijjař, tinni d tidett ǧant d tijjař.  
\v 4 Mařa ca n tajjač ɣares iḥenjiren niɣ ayyawen, ejj i-ten ad řemden d amezwar maḥend ad ggen min ittřiqen di ṭṭweɛ n řaǧ nsen, ad dd-arren i lwalidin min ttursen, minzi ddegga yusa-dd x řxaḍar n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 5:4 \xt Amz. 45:10, 11; Mt. 15:4; Mk. 7:10; Afa. 6:1, 2. \x*  
\v 5 Maca tajjač nican d tenni iǧan weḥḥdes, tessitim di AREBBI uca tṣebbar di tutra d tẓaǧitin, ǧiřet d wass. \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt Lk. 2:36; 1 Kur. 7:32. \x*  
\v 6 Maca tenni iwḍan di tudart n nnecwet, aqa temmut waxxa teddar.  
\v 7 Weṣṣa i-tent timesřayin-a, ḥima ad iřint břa řɛib.  
\v 8 Minzi mařa ca n yijj war itthilli ca di wi iǧan nnes, d amewaru deg yinni iǧan d aytbab n taddart n familya n yinni yumnen, aqa wanita immenḍar l’iman uca netta mahu x yinni war yuminen ca. \x ◘ \xo 5:8 \xt Gal. 6:10. \x*   
\m
\v 9 Ixḍar xenni ict n tajjač illa mařa ɣares zi settin n iseggʷusa ař tsawent, ict n tajjač nni tuɣa \add d tamɣart\add* n ijj n weryaz,  
\v 10 tenni ɣar teǧa cchadet aqa tegga řexdayem tiṣebḥanin: niɣ tesseymi iḥenjiren nnes, niɣ tareḥḥeb s ibarraniyyen, niɣ tessired iḍaren n imqeddasen, niɣ tewca fus i yinni ittwaḥṣaren, \add wah,\add* aqa tegga marra řxedmet taṣebḥant. \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Amz. 18:4; 19:2; Lk. 7:38,44; 1 Bṭ. 4:9. \x*   
\m
\v 11 Maca war qebbeř tijjař timeẓyanin, minzi nitenti ttexsent ad ssarxunt i Lmasiḥ s nnecwat nsent, arezzunt x ijj n weryaz.  
\v 12 Aqa ccreɛ nsent imten, minzi ssarsent l’iman nsent amezwar ɣar uɣezdis.  
\v 13 Maɣar nitenti ssřemdent \add inneɣni\add* řeɛqez am ggurent x tudrin, war iǧi ssřemdent waha řeɛgez, maca nitenti ttɛawadent řexburat, ttadfent di cɣuřat \add n midden\add*, qqarent min war icuwwaren. \x ◘ \xo 5:13 \xt Tit. 2:3. \x*  
\v 14 S uyenni xseɣ ad meřcent tijjař timeẓyanin, ad dd-jjent iḥenjiren, ad ssuyurent taddart nsen, war ttejjint ca i řeɛdu ssibbet ḥima ad iceqqef. \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt 1 Kur. 7:9. \x*  
\v 15 Minzi aqa ca \add zzaysent\add* bdant ad ffɣent abrid, ḍeffarent cciṭan.   
\m
\v 16 Mařa din iryazen niɣ timɣarin yumnen ɣarsen tijjař, ejj i-ten ad daysent thillan, maḥend war ittiři ddqeř ɛad x tmesmunt, ḥima \add tamesmunt\add* ad ɣares yiři maḥend ad tɛawen tinni iǧan d tijjař s tidett.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Imɣaren n tmesmunt  
\m
\v 17 Imɣaren nni ittḍebbaran mliḥ, sdahǧen aweqqar tnayen n imuren, abeɛda inni ixeddmen deg Wawař u deg useřmed. \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt Rum. 15:27; 1 Kur. 9:11; Gal. 6:6; Fil. 2:29; 1 Ts. 5:12; Ɛbr. 13:17. \x*  
\v 18 Minzi Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* qqarent: “War ttegg tacmant i uyenduz issarwaten!”, u: “Axeddam isdaheǧ řmunet nnes!” \x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt Lawi 19:13; Aɛwd. 24:14; 25:4; Mt. 10:10; Lk. 10:7; 1 Kur. 9:9. \x*  
\v 19 War qebbeř ca tanfuč ḍidd i umɣar, mɣir x uqemmum n tnayen niɣ n třata n řechud. \x ◘ \xo 5:19 \xt Aɛwd. 19:15. \x*  
\v 20 Inni ixḍan, ɛeyyeb i-ten zzat i marra, ḥima inneɣni ad ggʷeden ɛawed.  
\v 21 Ziyyareɣ xak zzat i AREBBI d Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ d lmalakat nnes ittwafarzen, ad teḥḍid man aya břa řfarz, war ttegg uřa d ict n tmesřact ɛlaḥsab udmawen. \x ◘ \xo 5:21 \xt Aɛwd. 17:4; 19:18; Rum. 1:9; 9:1; 2 Kur. 1:23; 11:31; Gal. 1:20; Fil. 1:8; 1 Ts. 2:5; 5:27; 1 Tim. 6:13. \x*  
\v 22 War ssrusa ifassen nnec x ḥed s uqeǧeq, war carrec di ddnub n inneɣni, ḥḍa ixef nnec di řeṣfayet. \x ◘ \xo 5:22 \xt Řex. 6:6; 8:17; 13:3; 19:6; 1 Tim. 4:14; 2 Tim. 1:6. \x*   
\m
\v 23 War sess aman waha, maca su drus n binu i stumaɣu nnec u i řeḥřac nnec azirar. \x ◘ \xo 5:23 \xt Izhd. 104:15. \x*   
\m
\v 24 Aqa din iwdan i ɣar iǧa ddnub nsen banen mliḥ deɣya, aqa \add ddnub nsen\add* ttizzaren asen ɣar ccreɛ, uca aqa din ca nneɣni ḍeffaren ten \add ddnub nsen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 5:24 \xt Gal. 5:19. \x*  
\v 25 Ammu dd-banent uřa d řexdayem tiṣebḥanin, maca \add uřa d\add* tinni i war iǧin ammu, war zemmarent ad qqiment nnuffarent.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Imsexxaren d aytbab nsen  
\m
\v 1 Ittxeṣṣa i marra inni iǧan sadu azayřu n tesmuɣi ad weqqaren aytbab nsen di marra, ḥima war ittiři uceqqef deg Yisem n AREBBI u di tɣuri nnes. \x ◘ \xo 6:1 \xt Afa. 6:5; Kul. 3:22; Tit. 2:9; 1 Bṭ. 2:18. \x*  
\v 2 Ejj \add isemɣan\add* nni ɣar iǧa imasen umnen war ten sseḥqirin ca, umi nitni d awmaten i iǧan. Maca s řɛeks ejj i-ten ad asen sexxaren \add mliḥ\add*, minzi nitni umnen u aqa aten d \add awmaten\add* iɛizzen, inni ɣarsen xeddmen nitni di řaman. Seřmed man aya u zeyyar xasen.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Lxaṭar n waṭṭas n wagřa  
\m
\v 3 Maca mařa din ḥed isseřmed ict n řḥajjet nneɣni uca war yareddef ca awařen iṣeḥḥen n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ d tɣuri x mammec icuwwar ad neɛbed AREBBI s tiggʷudi,  
\v 4 aqa netta ittuff am war issin walu, iweddar deg imḥarwaḍen d imcubbecen i-dd-ittawyen řeḥsed d umenɣi d uceqqef d ict n nneyyet d taɛeffant \x ◘ \xo 6:4 \xt 1 Tim. 1:4; 2 Tim. 2:23; Tit. 3:9. \x*  
\v 5 uřa d tamara i dd-yekkin zeg iwdan inni ittwaɣeccen di řeɛqeř nsen, tweddar asen ttidet, ittɣiř asen aqa arbeḥ iqqim ɣar tiggʷudi zi AREBBI. Beɛɛed xasen. \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt 1 Kur. 11:16. \x*  
\v 6 Maca arbeḥ nneɣ d ameqqran. Aqa-t d tiggʷudi zi AREBBI, \add am\add* ɣarneɣ min neḥdaj. \x ◘ \xo 6:6 \xt Awřn. 15:16; Ɛbr. 13:5. \x*  
\v 7 Minzi war dd-niwi walu ɣar ddunect uca aqa nessen war nzemmar akidneɣ neksi walu zzayes. \x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt Ayub 1:21; 27:19; Izhd. 49:18. \x*  
\v 8 S uyenni, mařa ɣarneɣ řmeɛteq d dduri, aqa neqneɛ. \x ◘ \xo 6:8 \xt Izhd. 55:23; Awřn. 27:26; Mt. 6:25; 1 Bṭ. 5:7. \x*  
\v 9 Maca inni ixsen ad ssmunen agřa, ad wḍan deg ijarriben u di řefxux u deg waṭṭas n nnecwat tifɣař ittḍarran, tinni ittejjan iwdan ad ɣarqen deg uteḥḥi d řekḥeḍ. \x ◘ \xo 6:9 \xt Awřn. 11:28; Mt. 13:22; Yaɛ. 5:1. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Minzi aẓwar n marra tuɛeffna aqa t d ṭṭmeɛ n tmenyat. Aqa din ca inni tuɣa ittmeẓřin di man aya, iweddar asen l’iman uca jebbden aṭṭas n tamara i yixef nsen. \x ◘ \xo 6:10 \xt Uf. 23:8; Aɛwd. 16:19; Awřn. 15:16. \x*   
\m
\v 11 Maca cek, a bnadem n AREBBI, arweř zi man aya uca arzu x tsegda, x tnicant, x l’iman, x tayri, x ṣṣbar u x temhint. \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt 2 Tim. 2:22. \x*  
\v 12 Mneɣ amenɣi aṣebḥan n l’iman, cebbar di Tudart ittduman nni umi ɣar dd-tᵉttwařaɣid, min xef tcehded cchadet taṣebḥant zzat i waṭṭas n řechud. \x ◘ \xo 6:12 \xt 1 Tim. 1:18. \x*  
\v 13 Cehhdeɣ i cek zzat i AREBBI, wenni iwcin Tudart i marra, u zzat i Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, wenni tuɣa icehhden cchadet taṣebḥant aṭṭas zzat i Punṭiyus Pilaṭus, \x ◘ \xo 6:13 \xt Aɛwd. 32:39; 1 Ṣm. 2:6; Mt. 27:11; Yḥ. 18:37; 1 Tim. 5:21. \x*  
\v 14 ḥima ad teḥḍid ttewṣeyyet břa ssuss niɣ řɛib ař dd ɣa iban Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.  
\v 15 Netta ad ittwasseḍhar di řweqt nnes: AREBBI ittwabarken, Amzemmar kuřci x marra min iǧan, Ajeǧid x \add marra\add* ijeǧiden d Sidi n isiditen, \x ◘ \xo 6:15 \xt 1 Tim. 1:17; Asa. 17:14; 19:16. \x*  
\v 16 Wenni weḥḥdes war ifennin, Wenni izeddɣen di tfawt i war izemmar ad ɣares yadef ḥed, Wenni war iẓri bnadem niɣ izemmar ɛad ad t iẓar, i Netta umi ɣar iǧa ccan d ṣṣulṭa i řebda qaɛ. Amin. \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt Uf. 33:20; Aɛwd. 4:12; 1 Yḥ. 4:12; 1 Tim. 1:17.\x*   
\m
\v 17 Ɛřem i aytbab n wagřa di ddunect-a war ttiřin d imɛeffaren, war ttcařen x wagřa war yarekknen, maca \add ad ttecřen\add* x AREBBI iddaren, wenni d aneɣ itticen marra timesřayin s ufeyyeḍ ḥima ad xaneɣ ifewwej, \x ◘ \xo 6:17 \xt Mk. 4:18; Lk. 8:14. \x*  
\v 18 uca \add ɛřem\add* i-ten ad ggen řexdayem iṣebḥen, ad ɣarsen iřint tmegga tiṣebḥanin, ad wejden maḥend ad wcen u ad carcen.  
\v 19 Ejj i-ten ad ssarsen \add ammu\add* dsas aṣebḥan i yixef nsen i řweqt i dd ɣa yasen, maḥend ad ɣarsen tiři Tudart d Tidett. \x ◘ \xo 6:19 \xt Mt. 6:20; Lk. 12:33; 16:9. \x*   
\m
\v 20 A Timutiyu, ḥḍa min d ac ittwawekkřen, aggʷej x řhard ixwan uřa x řɛekasat i dd-itteffɣen zi tussna issxarriqen. \x ◘ \xo 6:20 \xt 1 Tim. 1:4; 4:7; 2 Tim. 2:16; Tit. 1:14; 3:9. \x*  
\v 21 Aqa din ca n iwdan řami seɛfen man aya, semḥen di l’iman. Ad kidek yiři arḍa! Amin.   